Burlington Industries Inc said itfiled with the Securities and Exchange Commission registrationstatements covering two offerings of debt securities.    One issue will be 100 mln dlrs of sinking fund debenturesdue 2017. Proceeds will be used for general corporate purposes,including the reduction of short-term borrowings, acquisitions,stock repurchases and capital expenditures.    The other offering will be 75 mln dlrs of convertiblesubordinated debentures due 2012. Proceeds will be used toredeem the company's outstanding 8-3/4 pct convertiblesubordinated debentures of 2008, Burlington said. Reuter&#3;